snippet.title: [Selfmade] Touhou The Shattered Sky - Hard Mode 1cc (Reimu A)
snippet.description:
So here it is, my first real full game.
After 2 years of development... I WOULD WISH TO DELETE EVERYTHING AND REMAKE THIS!!!! ;_;
When I started this project, I didnt really know wtf I was doing and this hurt the game in the long run. A lot of things werent fixable anymore without unjustified work.
So here it is. See it as our "The last Comer"...

...and wait for our "Mystical Power Plant" =)
TH SoHW - Coming Soon ;)


Game download: http://www.bulletforge.org/u/eredom/p/the-shattered-sky


Staff: Me (Programming & Team Lead)
Music: DjAbner: https://www.youtube.com/c/DJAbner
Char Design: MeyMoonturret
Supportive Graphics: Danicky
Lunatic Balancing/Dialogue: Minogame https://www.youtube.com/user/Minogame1
Other Notewothy guys:
- Badz
- Naudiz
- Virtlux
